 ## News Summarization & Sentiment Analysis
ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project is a News Summarization & Sentiment Analysis tool built using Flask, Streamlit, and NLTK. It fetches the latest news articles for a given company, summarizes them, analyzes the sentiment, and provides a comparative sentiment distribution. It also supports Text-to-Speech (TTS) functionality in Hindi.

ğŸš€ Features

Fetch Latest News: Scrapes Bing News for articles related to a given company.

Summarization: Uses sumy library to generate a concise summary.

Sentiment Analysis: Uses nltk's SentimentIntensityAnalyzer to classify news as Positive, Negative, or Neutral.

Comparative Sentiment Analysis: Aggregates sentiment scores across multiple articles.

Text-to-Speech (TTS): Converts summaries into Hindi audio.

Streamlit UI: Provides an interactive web app for users.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Frontend: Streamlit

Backend: Flask (REST API)

Web Scraping: BeautifulSoup

Summarization: sumy (LSA Summarizer)

Sentiment Analysis: NLTK (VADER)

Text-to-Speech: gTTS
